| `#/admin/overview` | `SystemAdminLiveApp` overview workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Default admin landing route. |
| `#/admin/proof-dashboard` | Proof dashboard workspace | `SYSTEM_ADMIN` | Proof-scoped admin surface. |
